  (4083, 578, 'A shark''s attack is stimulated by the kind of splashing and activity that occurs whenever humans go swimming -- you can''t avoid it!', 'Hooper'),
  (4084, 578, 'There are only two ways to solve this thing: you can kill it, or you can cut off its food supply...', 'Hooper'),
  (4085, 578, 'If you''re so concerned about the beaches, you two, you do whatever you have to to keep them safe, but with you or without you, the beaches stay open this weekend.', 'Vaughn'),
  (4086, 578, 'Amity, y''know, means ''Friendship.', 'Vaughn'),
  (4087, 578, 'Jerry, come on in and look at this.', 'Director'),
  (4088, 578, 'Nothing from up here, Daisy.', 'Copter Spotter'),
  (4089, 578, 'It''s an authorization to employ a contractor.', 'Brody'),
  (4090, 578, 'Or do we do this on a handshake and a promise?', 'Quint'),
  (4091, 578, 'Put that blackfish on board, pump the bilges, and top off the fuel tanks, and finish up in the morning.', 'Quint'),
